T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"好耐無去潮流特區，原來搞成咁<br />\n鬼咩咁多商場舖仔都賣淘仔野，香港人大陸人都唔會買啦，做網舖咪又死，網舖一樣係淘仔貨，有分別咩"},{"pid":"5fc4dac088ce71027d51e9aecec7d366846f0d29","tid":494681,"uid":94739,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:24:43.000Z","msg":"自從有ig shop之後，都已經無乜係街睇衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多都係去試Size"},{"pid":"0f535dc7e261189644bbfb71bef47c371691b39c","tid":494681,"uid":22566,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"一定係因為佔中啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得呢句咋嘛佢地"},{"pid":"77171e8485d6b618c50e79fbaba0887f2842eecd","tid":494681,"uid":30006,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"多謝菜街班垃圾啦，嘈生晒搵鬼去"},{"pid":"0aa2841f4dac0320d4e8a6ee967f4ca8d2aa502c","tid":494681,"uid":121409,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"就嚟2018都仲提佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764ed58948585cbd553bf2847e0ce4f8bae0d3af","tid":494681,"uid":42435,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"五毛得一句＂佔中＂後遺症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52aa79e2e434bd3c61ea69bf41fcc2ea662c2229","tid":494681,"uid":56701,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:30:17.000Z","msg":"我都不知幾耐無行旺角，尤其夜晚，一諗起啲仆街大媽，同啲咸濕伯父，扮晒跳舞其實互相偕油，好自然毛管動!<br />\n旺角遲啲連仔都唔願去"},{"pid":"063c52a669c707237fab89abfe4a311819c7b8f9","tid":494681,"uid":119792,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:32:09.000Z","msg":"見到班大媽係到唱歌都唔想去啦"},{"pid":"46f5186538f29abf5bb7a48aed7f78c031d8257b","tid":494681,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你仲未知係網購因素，呢件記者炒咗佢啦</blockquote><br />\n呃稿費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167d1cb260fc1e049fb6dce0e59b0